Class SCDSResponse

java.lang.Object
com.redis.app.redis_app_studio.shared.SCDSResponse
public class SCDSResponse extends Object
Collection of utility methods focused on converting Foundation objects into SmartClient response payloads.

      public com.isomorphic.datasource.DSResponse create(com.redis.foundation.data.DataGrid aDataGrid, AppResource anAppResource, int aStartRow, int anEndRow, int aTotalRows)
      Creates a SmartClient data source response instance based on the data grid and row information. In addition, if the application resource is non-null, then it will be used to assign an App Studio context column for each row in the data source response.
      Parameters:
      aDataGrid - Data grid instance
      anAppResource - Application resource instance (can be null)
      aStartRow - Starting row offset
      anEndRow - Ending row offset
      aTotalRows - Total rows
      Returns:
      SmartClient data source instance
